      <div class="choice-detail">Sketch the Mars decay sequence as arrows: small size → fast core cooling → magnetic field loss → atmospheric stripping → liquid water loss → climate collapse. One arrow per causal step. Add one sentence under the diagram naming the criterion in your framework that captures each step.</div>
